have indeed received a command to bless;"},{"kind":"text","text":" since he has blessed, "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":1,"text":"Sam, LXX read since I will bless"},{"kind":"text","text":" I cannot change it."}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[{"marker":1,"text":"Sam, LXX read since I will bless"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Num:23:21","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"He considers no disaster for Jacob;"},{"kind":"text","text":" he sees no trouble for Israel. "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":1,"text":"Or He does not observe sin in Jacob; he does not see wrongdoing in Israel"},{"kind":"text","text":" The "},{"kind":"text","text":"Lord","style":"divine"},{"kind":"text","text":" their God is with them, "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Gn 28:15","book":"Gen","chapter":28,"verse":15,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Nm 14:9","book":"Num","chapter":14,"verse":9,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Dt 2:7","book":"Deu","chapter":2,"verse":7,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Dt 20:1","book":"Deu","chapter":20,"verse":1,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jos 1:17","book":"Jos","chapter":1,"verse":17,"letter":"e"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jdg 6:13","book":"Jdg","chapter":6,"verse":13,"letter":"f"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"2Ch 20:17","book":"2Ch","chapter":20,"verse":17,"letter":"g"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ps 46:11","book":"Psa","chapter":46,"verse":11,"letter":"h"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Is 8:10","book":"Isa","chapter":8,"verse":10,"letter":"i"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Is 41:10","book":"Isa","chapter":41,"verse":10,"letter":"j"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jr 1:19","book":"Jer","chapter":1,"verse":19,"letter":"k"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jr 15:20","book":"Jer","chapter":15,"verse":20,"letter":"l"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Zp 3:17","book":"Zep","chapter":3,"verse":17,"letter":"m"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Hg 2:4","book":"Hag","chapter":2,"verse":4,"letter":"n"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rv 21:3","book":"Rev","chapter":21,"verse":3,"letter":"o"},{"kind":"text","text":" and there is rejoicing over the King among them."}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Gn 28:15","book":"Gen","chapter":28,"verse":15},{"label":"Nm 14:9","book":"Num","chapter":14,"verse":9},{"label":"Dt 2:7","book":"Deu","chapter":2,"verse":7},{"label":"Dt 20:1","book":"Deu","chapter":20,"verse":1},{"label":"Jos 1:17","book":"Jos","chapter":1,"verse":17},{"label":"Jdg 6:13","book":"Jdg","chapter":6,"verse":13},{"label":"2Ch 20:17","book":"2Ch","chapter":20,"verse":17},{"label":"Ps 46:11","book":"Psa","chapter":46,"verse":11},{"label":"Is 8:10","book":"Isa","chapter":8,"verse":10},{"label":"Is 41:10","book":"Isa","chapter":41,"verse":10},{"label":"Jr 1:19","book":"Jer","chapter":1,"verse":19},{"label":"Jr 15:20","book":"Jer","chapter":15,"verse":20},{"label":"Zp 3:17","book":"Zep","chapter":3,"verse":17},{"label":"Hg 2:4","book":"Hag","chapter":2,"verse":4},{"label":"Rv 21:3","book":"Rev","chapter":21,"verse":3}],"footnotes":[{"marker":1,"text":"Or He does not observe sin in Jacob; he does not see wrongdoing in Israel"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Num:23:22","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"God brought them out of Egypt;"},{"kind":"text","text":" he is like the horns of a wild ox for them. "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":1,"text":"Or Egypt; they have the horns of a wild ox"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Nm 24:8","book":"Num","chapter":24,"verse":8,"letter":"a"}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Nm 24:8","book":"Num","chapter":24,"verse":8}],"footnotes":[{"marker":1,"text":"Or Egypt; they have the horns of a wild ox"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Num:23:23","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"There is no magic curse against Jacob"},{"kind":"text","text":" and no divination against Israel."},{"kind":"text","text":" It will now be said about Jacob and Israel,"},{"kind":"text","text":" “What great things God has done!”"}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Num:23:24","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"A people rise up like a lioness;"},{"kind":"text","text":" they rouse themselves like a lion. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Nm 24:9","book":"Num","chapter":24,"verse":9,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" They will not lie down until they devour the prey"},{"kind":"text","text":" and drink the blood of the slain."}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Nm 24:9","book":"Num","chapter":24,"verse":9}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Num:23:25","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Then Balak told Balaam, “Don’t curse them and don’t bless them!”"}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Num:23:26","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"But Balaam answered him, “Didn’t I tell you: Whatever the "},{"kind":"text","text":"Lord","style":"divine"},{"kind":"text","text":" says, I must do?” "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Nm 22:38","book":"Num","chapter":22,"verse":38,"letter":"a"}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Nm 22:38","book":"Num","chapter":22,"verse":38}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Num:23:27","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Again Balak said to Balaam, “Please come. I will take you to another place. Maybe it will be agreeable to God that you can put a curse on them for me there.” "}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Num:23:28","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"So Balak took Balaam to the top of Peor, which overlooks the wasteland. "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":1,"text":"Or overlooks Jeshimon"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Nm 21:20","book":"Num","chapter":21,"verse":20,"letter":"a"}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Nm 21:20","book":"Num","chapter":21,"verse":20}],"footnotes":[{"marker":1,"text":"Or overlooks Jeshimon"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Num:23:29","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Balaam told Balak, “Build me seven altars here and prepare seven bulls and seven rams for me.” "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Nm 23:1","book":"Num","chapter":23,"verse":1,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Nm 23:1","book":"Num","chapter":23,"verse":1}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Num:23:30","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"So Balak did as Balaam said and offered a bull and a ram on each altar."}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]}]},"cachedAt":1783279348645}